ernative=3F =E2=80=9CNo=E2=80=9D=3F You don=E2=80=99t get in that room by s=
aying no to Mohammed bin Salman.</p> <p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And while=
 Neom always seemed like a wild vanity project to=C2=A0<em>me</em>, I suppo=
se if you work on it you have to find a way for the math to work. Making th=
e math work, in this case, means achieving an internal rate of return of ab=
out 9%, significantly higher than the standard wild vanity project rate of =
negative infinity. One of the best-known facts about finance is that you ca=
n achieve any IRR that you want,=C2=A0<em>in a spreadsheet:</em></p> <block=
quote> <p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At Trojena, the planned ski resort, a f=
